# Skills Bridge

This project ships with universal Agent Skills installed via `npx skills add`, located at `.agents/skills/<skill-name>/SKILL.md`.

When the user's request matches a skill's trigger conditions (described in each skill's frontmatter `description`), READ and FOLLOW that skill's `SKILL.md` immediately — do not just acknowledge it.

## Available Skills

### `polish`
**Path:** `.agents/skills/polish/SKILL.md`

**Triggers:** user mentions "polish", "polir", "finalizar", "finishing touches", "pre-launch review", "going from good to great", "something looks off", or any final-quality-pass request.

**What it does:** Performs a meticulous final pass for alignment, spacing, typography, color/contrast, interaction states, micro-interactions, copy consistency, icons, forms, edge cases, responsiveness, performance, and code-quality cleanup.

**Important:** This skill explicitly references `/frontend-design` and `/teach-impeccable` as preparation steps. Those slash-commands are Claude Code conventions and may not exist in Cursor — when not available here, treat them as informational and proceed with the skill body, while substituting the project's existing design-system context (read `DESIGN.md` and `.cursor/rules/design-system.mdc` first to anchor the polish pass to the project's actual visual language).

### `influ-cinematic-landing`
**Path:** `.agents/skills/influ-cinematic-landing/SKILL.md`

**Triggers:** landing de onboarding, influ cinematic landing, página inicial cinematográfica para criadores, primeira visita editorial, onboarding full-screen da plataforma.

**What it does:** Landing cinematográfica estilo influencer/editorial — hero com stage de carrosséis, fluxo em 3 passos, montagem de capacidades e CTA para o studio. Implementação em `src/components/OnboardingLanding.jsx`; flag `vc_landing_done`.

### `carrossel-cultura`
**Path:** `.agents/skills/carrossel-cultura/SKILL.md`

**Auxiliary:** `.agents/skills/carrossel-cultura/html-template.md` (checklist HTML estático / export PNG fora da app).

**Triggers:** Tendência/Cultura, pacote criativo cultura, brandsdecoded, carrossel editorial viral, Instagram cultura, fenómeno cultural, triagem editorial, arco S1–S9, preset `tendencia_cultura`, alinhar prompts/copy ao formato editorial “fenómeno já percebido”, ou pedidos explícitos de carrossel viral no estilo deste pacote.

**What it does:** Valida tema como tendência/cultura (não “dica solta”); coleta inputs; triagem + 8 headlines; arco 9 slides (adaptável 6–12); liga o fluxo ao código em `ViralCarrossel.jsx` ou a HTML estático conforme `html-template.md`.

## How to invoke

If the user explicitly types `/polish`, `polish this`, "passa um polish", "dá uma polida", "finaliza", or similar, READ `.agents/skills/polish/SKILL.md` in full and execute its protocol against the target the user named (or the most-recently-edited UI surface if no target is given).

For **Tendência/Cultura** / editorial brandsdecoded, READ `.agents/skills/carrossel-cultura/SKILL.md` in full (and `html-template.md` when gerar HTML estático ou export fora da app). When trabalhar **dentro da app**, cruzar com `creativePreset === 'tendencia_cultura'` e funções relacionadas em `ViralCarrossel.jsx`.
